    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>Sukumar Ghorai works at Texas Instruments and currently working on <span class="caps">OMAP</span> platform and Linux drivers. He is having 10+ years industry experience on different <span class="caps">RTOS</span> and with different platforms. <br />
He has been contributing to the Linux kernel for <span class="caps">NAND</span>, <span class="caps">MMC</span>/SD and worked in bootloader for for <span class="caps">OMAP</span> platforms. He currently focusing on open source and looking on <span class="caps">OMAP</span> system level integration issues.</p>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
      
